title: 196: Training Camp Takeaways
itunes:title: 196: Training Camp Takeaways
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down last night's Hall of Fame game before revealing what they have seen while traveling to each training camp. The guys also react to the most recent injury news around the league.
